<h1> All About This Episode! </h1>

<%# On the episode show page, a user should see:

Episode date
A list of the guests who were on that episode
Each guest's name should link to the Guest Show page %>

<p> Episode Date: <%= @episode.date %></p>
<p>List of Guests: </p><% @episode.guests.each do |guest| %>
                          <%= link_to "#{guest.name}", guest_path(guest.id) %>
                        <% end %>
